		<title>高冷貓也擋不住誘惑？女子靈機一動用「貓薄荷」泡腳效果超靈 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/29/%e9%ab%98%e5%86%b7%e8%b2%93%e4%b9%9f%e6%93%8b%e4%b8%8d%e4%bd%8f%e8%aa%98%e6%83%91%ef%bc%9f%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%90%e9%9d%88%e6%a9%9f%e4%b8%80%e5%8b%95%e7%94%a8%e3%80%8c%e8%b2%93%e8%96%84%e8%8d%b7%e3%80%8d/</link>
		
